WEBVTT

1
00:00:11.344 --> 00:00:12.846
[gentle. poignant music playing]

2
00:00:20.478 --> 00:00:22.480
[heavy breathing]

3
00:00:24.941 --> 00:00:26.067
[Si-eun] <i>What I have to do</i>…

4
00:00:28.653 --> 00:00:30.572
<i>I have to catch everybody</i>…

5
00:00:31.156 --> 00:00:32.824
[muffled shouting]

6
00:00:32.907 --> 00:00:34.868
<i>…if they start to go over the cliff.</i>

7
00:00:36.619 --> 00:00:41.124
<i>I mean. if they're running</i>
<i>and they don't look where they're going</i>…

8
00:00:48.423 --> 00:00:50.842
<i>I have to come out from somewhere</i>
<i>and catch them.</i>

9
00:01:01.770 --> 00:01:03.313
[heavy breathing echoing]

10
00:01:06.232 --> 00:01:09.611
[Si-eun] <i>That's all I'd do all day.</i>

11
00:01:13.990 --> 00:01:15.867
[heavy breathing echoing]

12
00:01:21.748 --> 00:01:23.750
["Hero" by Meego playing]

13
00:01:39.891 --> 00:01:45.063
WEAK HERO:
CLASS 2

14
00:02:40.034 --> 00:02:41.703
[exhales]

15
00:02:41.786 --> 00:02:43.788
[emotional music playing]

16
00:02:48.209 --> 00:02:49.878
You really are a psycho.

17
00:02:54.215 --> 00:02:56.759
You should understand me. Si-eun-a.

18
00:03:07.061 --> 00:03:08.730
[breathing shakily]

19
00:03:20.575 --> 00:03:22.911
THURSDAY 26 OCTOBER

20
00:03:25.663 --> 00:03:26.873
[sighs]

21
00:03:27.874 --> 00:03:29.876
[breathing shakily]

22
00:03:32.295 --> 00:03:34.923
[woman] <i>Why do you think</i>
<i>you're unable to sleep well?</i>

23
00:03:37.967 --> 00:03:40.303
<i>You said that you were</i>
<i>having the same dream.</i>

24
00:03:42.055 --> 00:03:45.600
<i>Do you still…</i>
<i>not want to tell me what the dream is?</i>

25
00:03:51.272 --> 00:03:53.024
Dreams don't really matter.

26
00:04:01.866 --> 00:04:03.701
Do the sleeping pills work for you?

27
00:04:06.871 --> 00:04:07.872
Yeah.

28
00:04:08.665 --> 00:04:11.501
Hmm… Is that the truth. Si-eun?

29
00:04:15.463 --> 00:04:18.675
Well. I'll let your mother know
they're working.

30
00:04:20.718 --> 00:04:21.719
Doctor?

31
00:04:23.137 --> 00:04:24.138
Yes?

32
00:04:26.474 --> 00:04:28.643
I think I'm done with this session today.

33
00:04:32.647 --> 00:04:34.399
[poignant music playing]

34
00:04:36.693 --> 00:04:37.944
[door opens]

35
00:04:53.876 --> 00:04:55.878
[lively chatter]

36
00:04:58.715 --> 00:05:00.091
[horn honks]

37
00:05:03.594 --> 00:05:05.596
[horn playing "La Cucaracha"]

38
00:05:10.018 --> 00:05:12.020
[overlapping chatter]

39
00:05:25.366 --> 00:05:28.953
[boy 1] Hey. look. I'm serious. I'll
really kick it this time. Watch. watch.

40
00:05:29.037 --> 00:05:30.496
-[boy 2 yelps]
-[students cheer]

41
00:05:30.580 --> 00:05:31.873
-Yeah!
-[laughter]

42
00:05:31.956 --> 00:05:33.207
You got him!

43
00:05:33.291 --> 00:05:34.417
[boy 2] Are you okay?

44
00:05:34.500 --> 00:05:36.461
-[boy 3] Nice kick. bro!
-[boy 4] Did you see that?

45
00:05:36.544 --> 00:05:39.672
-[boy 4] That was so hardcore.
-[boy 5] My throw was better than yours.

46
00:05:40.840 --> 00:05:42.550
-What?
-Hey. Yeon Si-eun.

47
00:05:43.426 --> 00:05:45.053
Hey. Let him through.

48
00:05:51.768 --> 00:05:52.769
Who's that?

49
00:05:54.645 --> 00:05:57.231
[boy 1] <i>I heard he transferred here</i>
<i>after killing some kid.</i>

50
00:05:58.608 --> 00:06:01.110
<i>Even that ass Choi Hyo-man chickened out</i>
<i>and didn't mess with him.</i>

51
00:06:01.194 --> 00:06:03.196
[laughter and chatter]

52
00:06:04.113 --> 00:06:06.449
[boy 6] Wow. he must be
a freaking psychopath.

53
00:06:06.532 --> 00:06:08.785
-Yeah. I think so…
-[boy 1] Hey. hey. hey. hey. Shut up.

54
00:06:08.868 --> 00:06:11.913
-[coughs] It's Yeon Si-eun.
-[boy 7] But what about this guy?

55
00:06:11.996 --> 00:06:14.499
Watch your mouth. bro.
He might kill someone again.

56
00:06:15.333 --> 00:06:17.085
[boy 8] Hey. Let's go for a smoke.

57
00:06:18.211 --> 00:06:20.213
[boy 9] Fuck this. man. This is too scary.

58
00:06:21.464 --> 00:06:26.302
"I'D JUST BE
THE CATCHER IN THE RYE AND ALL."

59
00:06:26.386 --> 00:06:29.639
THE CATCHER IN THE RYE
BY J.D. SALINGER

60
00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:31.682
[bag jingling]

61
00:06:33.393 --> 00:06:34.477
[music stops]

62
00:06:34.560 --> 00:06:35.645
[boy 10] Oh.

63
00:06:36.813 --> 00:06:38.439
[boy 11] Jun-tae is fucking screwed.

64
00:06:42.068 --> 00:06:43.319
I… I'm sorry. I. um…

65
00:06:44.737 --> 00:06:47.490
I was kind of in a rush.
and I bumped you by mistake.

66
00:06:58.251 --> 00:07:00.253
[dynamic music playing]

67
00:07:05.216 --> 00:07:08.386
[boy 12] Another shift. Jun-tae?
You're busy today!

68
00:07:10.805 --> 00:07:12.140
[boy 13] Deliveries!

69
00:07:27.572 --> 00:07:28.573
[boy 15] Nice!

70
00:07:30.241 --> 00:07:31.617
[snoring softly]

71
00:07:36.205 --> 00:07:38.416
I grabbed whatever. and
smashed the guy right on his head…

72
00:07:38.499 --> 00:07:40.460
-[boy 15] Seo Jun-tae!
-Yes?

73
00:07:43.504 --> 00:07:46.174
You were supposed to get
me strawberry milk.

74
00:07:47.175 --> 00:07:48.885
-Huh?
-[students whispering]

75
00:07:48.968 --> 00:07:50.553
[boy 15] Hey. you little bitch.

76
00:07:50.636 --> 00:07:54.474
I told you to switch it up last week.
so why didn't you listen?

77
00:07:55.057 --> 00:07:55.892
Ah.

78
00:08:00.438 --> 00:08:01.689
S… strawberry.

79
00:08:04.484 --> 00:08:05.860
What's with the face?

80
00:08:07.904 --> 00:08:10.031
[scoffs] Too hard for you?

81
00:08:10.823 --> 00:08:14.202
Um… I… I'm sorry.
I had a brain fart for a second.

82
00:08:15.828 --> 00:08:17.622
I'll let it pass just this once.

83
00:08:18.873 --> 00:08:19.874
Hmm?

84
00:08:21.626 --> 00:08:22.627
Come on.

85
00:08:24.045 --> 00:08:26.547
I'm sorry.
I'll pay more attention next time.

86
00:08:26.631 --> 00:08:29.800
[boy 15] Okay. Good.
Bring your collected stuff later.

87
00:08:32.053 --> 00:08:33.304
iPhones.

88
00:08:34.013 --> 00:08:35.056
iPhones.

89
00:08:35.556 --> 00:08:36.474
[boy 15] Beat it.

90
00:08:38.017 --> 00:08:40.228
[boy 16] Ah. Jun-tae is so freaking cute.

91
00:08:40.311 --> 00:08:42.813
[boy 17] Keep it up. Jun-tae!
He's like a puppy.

92
00:09:02.542 --> 00:09:06.629
11TH GRADE. CLASS 4 PHONE COLLECTION TABLE

93
00:09:11.050 --> 00:09:12.134
YEON SI-EUN

94
00:09:12.218 --> 00:09:13.469
[Jun-tae] "Yeon Si-eun."

95
00:09:16.138 --> 00:09:18.724
TRANSFERRED LAST YEAR
NOT TO BE MESSED WITH

96
00:09:25.523 --> 00:09:27.191
It's right there. look!

97
00:09:28.734 --> 00:09:29.694
What?

98
00:09:30.945 --> 00:09:32.321
Oh! It does.

99
00:09:43.124 --> 00:09:44.041
[Jun-tae] Yeon Si-eun.

100
00:09:47.587 --> 00:09:48.713
Uh. hi.

101
00:09:50.131 --> 00:09:52.967
Um. I was wondering
what kind of phone you have.

102
00:09:54.802 --> 00:09:55.803
What?

103
00:09:56.596 --> 00:09:58.472
Oh. n… nothing. just. um…

104
00:09:59.181 --> 00:10:02.977
I was wondering if you could tell me
what kind of phone you're using right now.

105
00:10:03.060 --> 00:10:04.145
I'm curious.

106
00:10:06.147 --> 00:10:06.981
Why?

107
00:10:09.317 --> 00:10:10.985
Just… no reason.

108
00:10:15.990 --> 00:10:17.450
[sighs]

109
00:10:19.535 --> 00:10:21.203
WELCOME TO THE WORLD OF GO
EUNJANG BOARDROOM

110
00:10:21.287 --> 00:10:22.538
[boy] Ouch. Ouch. Take it easy!

111
00:10:24.123 --> 00:10:25.916
[Hyo-man] Fuck. is this everything?

112
00:10:27.251 --> 00:10:28.419
[sighs]

113
00:10:29.545 --> 00:10:32.965
Seems like you keep bringing me
less and less. Huh?

114
00:10:35.509 --> 00:10:36.802
[tuts] Meh.

115
00:10:37.428 --> 00:10:38.596
Fuck this.

116
00:10:43.517 --> 00:10:48.230
Everyone. I think
you all have the wrong idea.

117
00:10:48.314 --> 00:10:52.109
Do you? Everyone.
this is a fucking business we have here.

118
00:10:52.193 --> 00:10:54.028
A business. Yeah?

119
00:10:54.111 --> 00:10:56.447
You need to all start
working your asses off

120
00:10:56.530 --> 00:10:59.200
in order for me to keep you
safe here at Eunjang High.

121
00:10:59.283 --> 00:11:00.451
Get it?

122
00:11:00.951 --> 00:11:02.244
[boy 1 whimpering]

123
00:11:02.328 --> 00:11:06.582
[Hyo-man] But if your fucking performance
keeps dropping like this.

124
00:11:07.083 --> 00:11:09.960
there's no reason for me
to keep protecting you guys.

125
00:11:10.836 --> 00:11:13.964
[sighs] Chief Seo.
today you need to open the books.

126
00:11:14.048 --> 00:11:15.383
Show me that. yeah?

127
00:11:15.466 --> 00:11:19.679
If there's even one thing missing. you're
all going to get a freakin' beating today.

128
00:11:19.762 --> 00:11:20.638
[chuckles]

129
00:11:20.721 --> 00:11:22.682
-The… the book.
-[Hyo-man] Five. Four.

130
00:11:23.265 --> 00:11:26.060
-Three. come on. Two.
-[bully 1] Jun-tae-ya. be quick about it.

131
00:11:26.602 --> 00:11:28.437
-[Hyo-man] Ugh…
-[Jun-tae sighs]

132
00:11:28.521 --> 00:11:32.316
Wait. Chief Seo.
This looks like an important note here.

133
00:11:32.400 --> 00:11:35.611
-What do you mean?
-[Hyo-man] I mean. look at this.

134
00:11:36.654 --> 00:11:38.823
"Classroom Four.
Yeon Si-eun. not to be messed with."

135
00:11:38.906 --> 00:11:40.491
Not to be messed with?

136
00:11:41.200 --> 00:11:42.118
[scoffs]

137
00:11:42.201 --> 00:11:43.828
-Why not?
-[sighs]

138
00:11:43.911 --> 00:11:47.373
Well… well. the thing is that. um…

139
00:11:47.456 --> 00:11:51.544
When he transferred here.
he almost got into a fight with you.

140
00:11:51.627 --> 00:11:54.964
but then everything was called off
when the teacher walked in.

141
00:11:55.047 --> 00:11:56.215
You told everyone.

142
00:11:56.799 --> 00:12:00.511
You said you'd take care of him yourself.
so nobody else should override you.

143
00:12:00.594 --> 00:12:02.513
-Get to the point. Hurry up.
-[Jun-tae] Yes. okay.

144
00:12:02.596 --> 00:12:04.390
Y… you haven't taken any measures yet.

145
00:12:04.473 --> 00:12:08.978
so I thought that if I would've
made a decision and moved ahead.

146
00:12:09.061 --> 00:12:10.938
it could create a problem

147
00:12:11.021 --> 00:12:13.607
-Problem. huh?
-[bully 1 scoffs] A problem.

148
00:12:13.691 --> 00:12:14.942
[bully 2] This crazy kid.

149
00:12:15.025 --> 00:12:16.527
[scoffs] Problem. huh?

150
00:12:16.610 --> 00:12:17.862
[laughs]

151
00:12:17.945 --> 00:12:20.448
[bully 2] Stupid kid
just pushed the worst button.

152
00:12:23.534 --> 00:12:25.661
-What problem is that?
-I… I misspoke. I think.

153
00:12:25.745 --> 00:12:27.830
[Hyo-man] So. by this so-called "problem."

154
00:12:27.913 --> 00:12:31.500
do you mean my ass is gonna
get owned by that little shit?

155
00:12:31.584 --> 00:12:33.127
-No. No.
-Is that what you really meant?

156
00:12:33.210 --> 00:12:34.462
Stop denying it. you bitch!

157
00:12:34.545 --> 00:12:35.588
You know how to block?

158
00:12:36.422 --> 00:12:39.175
Hey. that was pretty cool. man.
Do it again. keep going.

159
00:12:43.220 --> 00:12:44.054
Attention.

160
00:12:45.222 --> 00:12:46.390
[grunts]

161
00:12:48.684 --> 00:12:50.561
You must've kept that
to yourself for a while.

162
00:12:50.644 --> 00:12:52.688
That I'd lose. you stupid piece of shit!

163
00:12:52.772 --> 00:12:55.441
Right? Right? Hey! Hey! Hey!

164
00:12:55.941 --> 00:12:57.401
[Jun-tae whimpers]

165
00:12:58.527 --> 00:12:59.695
[Hyo-man] Get up.

166
00:12:59.779 --> 00:13:01.530
-Okay?
-[laughing]

167
00:13:01.614 --> 00:13:03.032
[boy 2 whimpers]

168
00:13:03.115 --> 00:13:04.450
[coughs]

169
00:13:05.242 --> 00:13:08.329
[Hyo-man] This kid looks hella fucked up.
You a beggar or what?

170
00:13:08.412 --> 00:13:11.749
You need to look sharp in your uniform.
Who did this to you. huh?

171
00:13:14.001 --> 00:13:15.169
[sighs]

172
00:13:15.252 --> 00:13:16.212
Sweep the leg.

173
00:13:16.796 --> 00:13:17.838
[bully 1] Oh. yeah!

174
00:13:18.506 --> 00:13:20.216
[bully 2] You nailed him!

175
00:13:20.299 --> 00:13:21.467
Oh. fuck.

176
00:13:21.550 --> 00:13:23.010
[laughing]

177
00:13:25.304 --> 00:13:26.430
[Hyo-man] Chief Seo.

178
00:13:26.514 --> 00:13:28.057
[Jun-tae trembling]

179
00:13:29.225 --> 00:13:30.684
I'll trust you.

180
00:13:30.768 --> 00:13:33.270
Bring Yeon Si-eun's punk-ass phone
to me today.

181
00:13:33.813 --> 00:13:35.397
-Okay.
-[boy 1 whimpers]

182
00:13:35.481 --> 00:13:36.941
[Hyo-man] Great. thank you.

183
00:13:38.400 --> 00:13:39.819
[boy 2 sobbing]

184
00:13:40.778 --> 00:13:43.656
[teacher] Both of you still
haven't done your homework?

185
00:13:43.739 --> 00:13:46.367
-These kids. They never listen.
-[PA chiming]

186
00:13:47.576 --> 00:13:49.411
Sir. I'm here for the phones.

187
00:13:49.495 --> 00:13:52.122
Huh? There's no ending announcement today.

188
00:13:52.915 --> 00:13:54.959
-See you tomorrow.
-Uh-huh. Great.

189
00:13:56.168 --> 00:13:58.170
[loud chatter outside]

190
00:13:59.255 --> 00:14:00.589
[Jun-tae] I can't help it.

191
00:14:01.924 --> 00:14:03.926
[suspenseful music playing]

192
00:14:05.261 --> 00:14:06.929
[Jun-tae] I have no other choice.

193
00:14:18.899 --> 00:14:20.025
[sighs]

194
00:14:21.235 --> 00:14:22.778
[breathing shakily]

195
00:14:26.073 --> 00:14:30.995
12 - YEON SI-EUN

196
00:14:31.078 --> 00:14:32.872
-[boy 1] Uh-huh?
-[boy 2] That's really…

197
00:14:32.955 --> 00:14:34.957
Yeah. Why don't you fly through Seoul?

198
00:14:35.457 --> 00:14:37.835
Let's hurry and get our phones. Then…

199
00:14:37.918 --> 00:14:39.128
-We'll stay and…
-[boy 1] Deal.

200
00:14:39.211 --> 00:14:41.714
Guys. take your phones.
There's no roll call today.

201
00:14:41.797 --> 00:14:43.507
[cheering and yelling]

202
00:14:54.268 --> 00:14:55.394
[boy 2] Hey. wait for me.

203
00:15:03.068 --> 00:15:03.986
[Si-eun] Hey.

204
00:15:05.613 --> 00:15:06.614
[Jun-tae] Huh?

205
00:15:07.406 --> 00:15:08.449
Why is my phone missing?

206
00:15:11.285 --> 00:15:12.745
Oh. your phone's not there?

207
00:15:14.413 --> 00:15:15.289
It's missing.

208
00:15:17.708 --> 00:15:19.251
Oh. really? [chuckles]

209
00:15:19.335 --> 00:15:21.962
Oh. Well. that's really weird. right?

210
00:15:22.046 --> 00:15:24.757
[laughs] Where did it go? How…

211
00:15:24.840 --> 00:15:26.300
Could it… It's not…

212
00:15:26.800 --> 00:15:27.927
It really isn't there.

213
00:15:28.010 --> 00:15:30.930
Oh. whoa. Wow. so strange.

214
00:15:31.013 --> 00:15:33.891
I just collected them
from the teachers' office.

215
00:15:33.974 --> 00:15:36.518
It's not like
I passed them out to everyone.

216
00:15:36.602 --> 00:15:38.771
You saw. right?
Everyone took their own phones.

217
00:15:38.854 --> 00:15:43.317
It'd be impossible for me to put my hands
on. look. or steal a… anyone's phone.

218
00:15:43.400 --> 00:15:45.903
[chuckles] I'm not a beggar or anything.

219
00:15:45.986 --> 00:15:48.447
[laughs nervously] Yeah.

220
00:15:49.406 --> 00:15:50.908
You know what I mean. right?

221
00:15:54.578 --> 00:15:56.622
No. I don't know what you meant at all.

222
00:15:57.414 --> 00:15:58.290
Um…

223
00:16:00.292 --> 00:16:02.419
Anyway. I have no idea
where your phone is.

224
00:16:02.503 --> 00:16:03.587
Okay.

225
00:16:06.340 --> 00:16:08.342
[footsteps retreating]

226
00:16:14.723 --> 00:16:16.517
[Jun-tae] Here. It's Yeon Si-eun's.

227
00:16:16.600 --> 00:16:18.352
[bully 1] I knew you'd do it. Chief Seo.

228
00:16:18.435 --> 00:16:20.729
Why'd it take him getting mad
for you to do it?

229
00:16:20.813 --> 00:16:22.606
You should've taken initiative.

230
00:16:23.232 --> 00:16:25.275
Clock out. I'll give this to Hyo-man.

231
00:16:26.485 --> 00:16:28.404
-Okay.
-[bully 2] Get home safe. Jun-tae.

232
00:16:28.487 --> 00:16:29.822
-Thanks.
-[bully 2 sniffs]

233
00:16:30.906 --> 00:16:31.907
Bye now.

234
00:16:33.283 --> 00:16:34.493
Love you. Jun-tae.

235
00:16:39.915 --> 00:16:41.458
[sighs]

236
00:16:48.924 --> 00:16:51.093
Hey. Si-eun. Did you find your phone?

237
00:17:05.816 --> 00:17:07.985
Uh… I. uh…

238
00:17:08.902 --> 00:17:10.320
I've been thinking.

239
00:17:10.404 --> 00:17:12.072
I've been feeling kind of bad.

240
00:17:12.698 --> 00:17:15.826
Well. some regrets. [chuckles]

241
00:17:15.909 --> 00:17:20.122
Because I'm partially responsible
for your missing phone.

242
00:17:20.205 --> 00:17:23.292
So if you're planning to get a new phone.

243
00:17:23.375 --> 00:17:25.627
I can chip in some of the money.

244
00:17:26.503 --> 00:17:30.507
Hey. this is the time for you to remain
positive and keep pushing forward. right?

245
00:17:30.591 --> 00:17:32.259
Anyway. as you may already know.

246
00:17:32.342 --> 00:17:34.595
some things
